OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with some patchy rain,
OL,6,Fthis mostly across the west. Becoming
OL,7,Fsomewhat drier this afternoon.
OL,8,FBrighter spells possible around
OL,9,FInverness. Some misty low cloud along
OL,10,Fthe west coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome rain or drizzle across
OL,13,Fthe north and west at times overnight.
OL,14,FDrier in the east with a few cloud
OL,15,Fbreaks around the Moray Firth. West
OL,16,Fcoast mist.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
