OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCloudy start with some
OL,6,Fdrizzle in the west. Otherwise
OL,7,Fbecoming largely dry with some
OL,8,Fsunshine breaking through in the east
OL,9,Fwhere it will become very warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry,
OL,12,Fsome warm sunshine in east Thursday,
OL,13,Fcloudier with some rain in west. Dry
OL,14,Fstart in east Friday otherwise cloud
OL,15,Fand rain spreading east. Dry, quite
OL,16,Fcloudy Saturday, brighter west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
